## 2. Acceptance criteria

- [ ] `pnpm install` clean, no peer-dependency warnings escalated
- [ ] `pnpm turbo run build lint typecheck test` green across all packages
- [ ] Cross-package imports go through workspace deps (no relative `../../packages/...`)
- [ ] Each publishable package has its own `README.md` + `LICENSE`
- [ ] Pinned tool versions match across the workspace (TypeScript, Node, etc.)

## 3. Non-goals

- No mixing of bundle formats — all packages emit ESM (`"type": "module"`)
- No transitive workspace deps in `dependencies` of published packages
  (use `peerDependencies` for shared workspace libs that consumers should bring)

